ike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f09bd3db62b37d3cc544a23e74f94a014d6bb4b9","tid":2331363,"uid":146299,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T17:34:39.000Z","msg":"因為我最近跑步都跑到膝頭痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔知點算好"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T17:37:52.000Z","msg":"係咪跑斜路<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 以前我都會膝頭痛 跑得太多斜路"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T17:47:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T18:53:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e62375c5a67432c5fde3d26b50481d5035b771ff","tid":2331363,"uid":38121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d8aef0e5d3437b71ee84890cf3c0e1817325affe","tid":2331363,"uid":89116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T17:20:32.000Z","msg":"平時有跑開步 一個星期一次 最近跑步唔知點解腓骨肌嗰個位勁痛 跑完之後嗰兩三日行路要拐下拐下 依家追巴士用小小力嗰個位就痛 有無人試過咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/drbao.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/%E6%8A%95%E5%BD%B1%E7%89%8701.jpeg?w=2000&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fdrbao.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F11%2F%25E6%258A%2595%25E5%25BD%25B1%25E7%2589%258701.jpeg%3Fw%3D2000%26ssl%3D1&h=78e03a0c&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T20:44:37.000Z","msg":"呢種應該係shin splint，我早排試過<br />\n你要拉多啲soleus同gastro，<br />\n停跑2個星期，直到唔痛先慢慢跑，分幾個星期漸進返去你本來嘅訓練量同強度，前題係跑嘅時候唔可以痛。<br />\n成因可能係對鞋唔啱，腳掌落地落唔好，突然跑得太多或太快<br />\n<br />\n詳細建議你問physio，但shin splint係冇得醫，只可以休息同做返啱啲跑姿"},{"pid":"0cb788e137f6aabda3fa81d50026cd8fe306e5b2","tid":2331363,"uid":318720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f09bd3db62b37d3cc544a23e74f94a014d6bb4b9","tid":2331363,"uid":146299,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"47a042015fb2bef28d3746fa9fd274afe534c0e5","tid":2331363,"uid":327999,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4da23f00dd7c